{"tid":982430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"坐飛機買到3機位　竟全被逼坐地板","createTime":"2019-01-15T06:23:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-15T21:07:54.000Z","uid":130626,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9e7ca4c647f4d1784b8a4fc065ae83555ac191c4","tid":982430,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T06:23:41.000Z","msg":"英國一名44歲婦人泰勒(Paula Taylor)，去年6月與全家人一起到西班牙度假，並向途易航空管理公司(TUI Airline Management)購買機票，她按照正常流程買了3張票，還提早3小時到機場報到登機。但泰勒一家人登機全傻眼，他們買的3個座位全部「消失」，整段航程被迫坐地板。<br />\n據英國《BBC》報導，泰勒太太花了1300英鎊(約新台幣52000元)，買了41DEF三座位的票。但等他們登機時，卻發現這3個座位竟然消失，空服員要求他們全家坐在地板上，也就是飛機上的「備用位置」，讓泰勒夫婦啼笑皆非。泰勒太太也表示，地板座位相當骯髒，她事後也要求航空公司退票，但航空公司並未對這起事件留下紀錄，並指願意賠償30英鎊(約新台幣1200元)，讓她相當不滿。之後泰勒夫婦投訴到BBC節目部，事件被報導出來後，航空公司立刻改變態度，願意全數賠款。<br />\n航空公司解釋，因為在起飛前最後一刻更改飛機，才會導致有乘客買到票、卻沒位可坐的窘境，航空公司願意向泰勒一家道歉，承認在處理上有疏失。不過英國民航局則表示，讓乘客在沒有座位的情況下登機飛行，是屬於違法的，目前正展開調查。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190115/640_c400d31d2e3200bd88a8c0533041ccc3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190115%2F640_c400d31d2e3200bd88a8c0533041ccc3.jpg&h=c9ea309f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190115/640_14ca342a0b8b07b6e89baf345777344d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190115%2F640_14ca342a0b8b07b6e89baf345777344d.jpg&h=c895d75c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c35b30216240ed2e300d23223499ebb492c57fcb","tid":982430,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T06:28:02.000Z","msg":"估錯地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abf2e17e57a8fda56cf77b68faf0c293e040b14a","tid":982430,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T19:17:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3f16cf49166e875e05daca76d5fc465d3e4d9a00","tid":982430,"uid":13953,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T19:22:02.000Z","msg":"個男人隔離有個空位？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"209f7789bceaa770b8efb0da9a1899dcdf0973b5","tid":982430,"uid":97240,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T19:26:24.000Z","msg":"班機個captain<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3c69cac497bd2a1284a62818ce7ca8ddd542223","tid":982430,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f16cf49166e875e05daca76d5fc465d3e4d9a00","tid":982430,"uid":13953,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T19:22:02.000Z","msg":"個男人隔離有個空位？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T20:05:02.000Z","msg":"唔係訂個個位冇得坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e98dc60714892148d13d29c332ac020e6f72390","tid":982430,"uid":55113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f16cf49166e875e05daca76d5fc465d3e4d9a00","tid":982430,"uid":13953,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T19:22:02.000Z","msg":"個男人隔離有個空位？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T20:32:42.000Z","msg":"可能去左廁所呢"},{"pid":"036d0de560d499c59c2207777bfc07aaadb6a2f5","tid":982430,"uid":79481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f16cf49166e875e05daca76d5fc465d3e4d9a00","tid":982430,"uid":13953,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T19:22:02.000Z","msg":"個男人隔離有個空位？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T21:07:54.000Z","msg":"去左廁所<br />\n<br />\n或者去左伸展下唔俾架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}